U

unlock() - Method in class com.zpaper.commons.utils.DynamicKeyLock
 
Utils - Class in com.zpaper.commons.utils
General purpose utilities for Zippi.File

The zPaper dbID returned by newID(int, String) and helpers is defined as follows:

<User ID><Uniquer><Timestamp> Where:
User IDAn 8 character hexadecimal string representing the of a userID padded with leading '0' characters Uniquer A single character which assists in the conflict avoidance by server/services location.
